---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Ruumide rentimine Tallinnas Hingamiskeskuses">

<!-- HEADER -->
<header class="header">
  <a href="/" class="header__logo">
    <img src="/images/logo.svg" alt="Hingamiskeskus" height="30" />
  </a>
  <div class="header__right">
    <a href="/e-pood" class="header__cart" aria-label="Ostukorv">
      <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <path d="M6 2L3 6v14a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V6l-3-4z"/><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/><path d="M16 10a4 4 0 01-8 0"/>
      </svg>
    </a>
    <button class="header__burger" aria-label="Menüü">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </button>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- HERO SECTION -->
<section class="float-hero">
  <div class="float-hero__content">
    <div class="float-hero__text">
      <h1 class="float-hero__title">Ruumide rent</h1>
      <p>Hingamiskeskuses pakume hubaseid ja harmoonilisi ruume, mis on loodud toetama sügavat lõdvestumist, sisemist rahu ja ühendust iseendaga. Meie keskuse atmosfäär on ideaalne erinevate teadlikkuse ja enesearengu praktikate jaoks.</p>
      <p>Ruumide rent toimub kokkuleppel. Kui soovid ruume rentida, täida palun allolev kontaktivorm, märkides ära oma soovid ja eelistatud kuupäevad. Eelistame pikaajalisi kliente, kes soovivad ruume regulaarselt kasutada.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="float-hero__media">
      <img src="/images/hoone.jpg" alt="Hingamiskeskus ruumide rent" class="float-hero__img" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA SECTION -->
<section class="float-cta">
  <h2 class="float-cta__title">Ruumide rent</h2>
  <a href="mailto:Info@hingamiskeskus.ee" class="float-cta__btn">TÄIDA VORM</a>
</section>

<!-- ROOMS -->
<section class="float-info">
  <h2 class="float-info__heading">Suur saal 38m2</h2>
  <p>Meie 38 m² suurune saal on ideaalne erinevateks sündmusteks, pakkudes avarust ja mugavust. Ruumis on olemas pleedid, padjad ja madratsid, et luua mugav ja lõõgastav keskkond nii istuvateks kui ka lamavateks tegevusteks. See teeb ruumi sobivaks töötubade, koolituste ja grupikohtumiste jaoks, kus on oluline mugavus ja võimalus lõõgastuda.</p>
  <p><strong>Hind: 25€/h +km.</strong></p>

  <h2 class="float-info__heading float-info__heading--spaced">Väike tuba 11m2</h2>
  <p>Meie 11 m² suurune tuba on hubane ja privaatne koht, mis sobib ideaalselt individuaalseteks seanssideks või väiksemateks kohtumisteks. Ruumis on väike voodi, kaks tooli, laud ning riiulid. Hubane valgustus loob sooja ja meeldiva õhkkonna, mis toetab keskendumist ja rahulikku olemist.</p>
  <p><strong>Hind: 7€/h +km.</strong></p>

  <p style="margin-top: 24px;">Aja broneerimiseks jäta meile oma kontaktandmed ja võtame Sinuga ise ühendust: <a href="mailto:Info@hingamiskeskus.ee" class="float-info__link">Info@hingamiskeskus.ee</a></p>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer class="footer">
  <div class="location">
    <h3 class="location__title">Aadress</h3>
    <p class="location__address">Sõle 14c, Tallinn</p>
    <img src="/images/hoone.jpg" alt="Hingamiskeskus Sõle 14c" class="location__photo" loading="lazy" />
  </div>
  <div class="footer__main">
    <img src="/images/logo-valge.png" alt="Hingamiskeskus" class="footer__logo" />
    <div class="footer__contact">
      <h3>Kontakt</h3>
      <p>E-post: Info@hingamiskeskus.ee</p>
      <p>Telefoninumber:</p>
      <p>+372 56695898</p>
      <p>+372 56497689</p>
      <p>(klienditugi 10.00-17.00)</p>
      <p>Hingamises OÜ</p>
      <p>EE147700771009732310</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer__hours">
      <h3>Lahtiolekuajad</h3>
      <p>E-R 8.30 - 20.00</p>
      <p>L-P 11.00 - 18.00</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer__social">
      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Hingamiskeskus" aria-label="Facebook" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/hingamiskeskus/" aria-label="Instagram" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1.5" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer__legal">
      <a href="/privaatsuspoliitika">Privaatsuspoliitika</a> | <a href="/muugitingimused">Müügitingimused</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* HEADER */
  .header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    background: #fff;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }
  .header__logo img { height: 28px; width: auto; }
  .header__right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
  .header__cart { color: #1d1e20; }
  .header__burger {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 5px;
    padding: 4px;
  }
  .header__burger span {
    display: block;
    width: 22px;
    height: 2px;
    background: #1d1e20;
  }

  /* HERO */
  .float-hero {
    background: #f3fcff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
  }
  .float-hero__content {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .float-hero__title {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: #1d1e20;
  }
  .float-hero__text p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #1d1e20;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .float-hero__img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .float-cta {
    background: #1f6d85;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 24px;
  }
  .float-cta__title {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .float-cta__btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #1d1e20;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  /* INFO / CONTENT */
  .float-info {
    background: #f3fcff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .float-info p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #1d1e20;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .float-info p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .float-info__heading {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: #1d1e20;
  }
  .float-info__heading--spaced {
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
  .float-info__link {
    color: #1f6d85;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* LOCATION */
  .location {
    background: #f3fcff;
    padding: 40px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .location__title {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .location__address {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .location__photo {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 600px;
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  .footer__main {
    background: #1d1e20;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 40px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .footer__logo {
    width: 180px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .footer__contact, .footer__hours {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .footer__contact h3, .footer__hours h3 {
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .footer__contact p, .footer__hours p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }
  .footer__social {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .footer__social a { color: #fff; }
  .footer__legal {
    font-size: 12px;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }
  .footer__legal a { color: #fff; text-decoration: none; }

  /* DESKTOP */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .header { padding: 12px 40px; }
    .header__logo img { height: 36px; }

    .float-hero { padding: 48px 40px; }
    .float-hero__content {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 40px;
    }
    .float-hero__text {
      flex: 1;
    }
    .float-hero__media {
      flex: 1;
    }
    .float-hero__title { font-size: 36px; }
    .float-hero__img { margin-top: 0; }

    .float-info { padding: 40px; }
    .float-cta { padding: 56px 40px; }
    .float-cta__title { font-size: 30px; }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .float-hero__title { font-size: 40px; }
    .float-hero { padding: 56px 40px; }
  }
</style>
